{"tid":1605466,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我們的世界，比電影更真實：《V煞》金句重溫","createTime":"2019-09-30T09:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:03:51.000Z","uid":8241,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"85f018ac74c848d0968324bbf55ccb9150e67420","tid":1605466,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:52:52.000Z","msg":"呢套05年電影 當年睇呢套戲無咩感覺 仲唔覺得特別好睇<br />\n但今日再重溫一次 感觸流淚 亦都有一種熱血感<br />\n重溫一下金句 成為我地鬥爭堅持嘅理念<br />\n為自由而戰 賀佢老母 <br />\n聽日見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「製造恐懼，是政府的終極武器。」</span><br />\n製造對立、分化，營造恐懼、渲染混亂，這就是攻心不見血，誘使人們團結在自己周圍的武器。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「藝術家藉謊言道出真相，而政客用謊言掩蓋真相。」</span><br />\n權貴要控制思想，古惑人心，首要就是控制傳媒，尤其是最有影響力的電視台。《V煞》裡，人人都知電視新聞說謊，粉飾太平，卻人人都要看電視。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」</span><br />\n一個人不能成事，更重要是集體的意志，每個個體的覺醒。懷著抗爭的心，靜以待時。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」</span><br />\n是的，持久的抗爭、萬馬齊瘖的鬱悶，容易令人心理變態，要保持身心健康，我們需要音樂、舞蹈、藝術、文學、遠足、毅行、多吸幾口新鮮空氣，政總門外最好放一個鋼琴。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「面具之下不是血肉之軀，面具之下是理念，理念是不怕子彈的。」</span><br />\n血肉之軀會逝，理念卻不死。改變，不爭朝夕，V煞一等二十年。<br />\n<br />\n《V煞》裡，有句對白，最觸動我。女主角在牢房裡，絕望中，讀到一封前人留下的信︰<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\">「我們的尊嚴不值多少錢，但它卻是我們真正擁有的。它是我們最後的一寸領地，在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。這寸心，是那麼小、那麼脆弱，卻是這世上最值得擁有的東西。我們決不能失去或放棄它。我們決不能讓別人奪走它。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-%E6%AF%94%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E6%9B%B4%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6-v%E7%85%9E-%E9%87%91%E5%8F%A5%E9%87%8D%E6%BA%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C-%25E6%25AF%2594%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AF%25A6-v%25E7%2585%259E-%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%258F%25A5%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25BA%25AB%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZnbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=bf59d4fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C-%25E6%25AF%2594%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AF%25A6-v%25E7%2585%259E-%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%258F%25A5%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25BA%25AB%2F&h=2dda8a75\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-%E6%AF%94%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E6%9B%B4%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%A6-v%E7%85%9E-%E9%87%91%E5%8F%A5%E9%87%8D%E6%BA%AB/</a>"},{"pid":"ce4ffb44d210a91af7362a2e5dc944537bd9676d","tid":1605466,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"Netfilx有得睇 歡迎大家未睇嘅可以睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31ba0f9ad80258a59f6fc3d9bd62a28f3fe285a","tid":1605466,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"聽日 賀佢老母"},{"pid":"0e989ee7f604f7cfa9ad9d161ad2c88dcf5aa746","tid":1605466,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f641e282bc77c9d18702f22ffd19ca5ea1839a","tid":1605466,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"堅持信念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff3b65856ddb6cda3ae97d17e5b6efe05ad2312","tid":1605466,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"香港人唔會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif